    "John Trapp": "Unto the fellowship ] Union being the ground of communion: so that all is in him is for us. I give my goods to the saints, saith David `[char_David_Rut_4]`, in the person of Christ.\nVer.\n9. Unto the fellowship] Union being the ground of communion: so that all is in him is for us. I give my goods to the saints, saith David `[char_David_Rut_4]`, in the person of Christ.\nVer."
